to run the tool:

change the limit input (ddata and ssignal) on doWP.cc

change the mass point you want to run on fits_4body.sh

then just do

. ./fits_4body.sh

it will create subfolders with plots/root files with WS and combine results / log files of doWP.C and combine

it will store limits in 3 versions

 - two btag categories combined 
 - two btag categories combined -- without systematics
 - only 2btag category
